    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Generate short videos with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive and log the results\n\n**Pattern:** Video Production · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nGenerate short videos with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive and log the results. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual shorts is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Read Content Calendar (Google Sheets) → Due for Publishing? → Post One at a Time → Count Published → Align Field Names → Cap Batch Volume → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to video production without manual effort\n- Anyone automating shorts in content creation\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Improves response time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "4f88ec10-881b-23fc-5325-6f7fde08276f",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
